Maybe you knew, maybe you didn’t: WE MAKE ICE CREAM NOW!!!! Only currently  available at our 2209 Magazine location and our new sister concept @districtalldaydelicious at 611 Okeefe (give them a follow while you’re at it).

That last post was unfair. Y’all wanna know “what kind of ice cream”, so here’s a little taste. Pictured is our add-ins for one of our newest rotations, “Winter Forest” - it’s a pine ice cream base (yep, like the tree), Black Forest cake, candied oranges, and white non pereils (the little things on sno-caps). Tastes like the Winter we can only imagine down here.

I started a very long post about this and then realized you wouldn’t read it. TLDR - vegetarian burger is back, we make this bad boy from scratch with like 20 ingredients, it’s very very good, this is not that weird “maybe it’s meat” stuff.

Incoming shameless plug for @districtalldaydelicious because, you know, reach. 

District All Day Delicious is brought to you by the same team that brought you…. us (we have a thing for long confusing names). 

At DADD you’ll find many of the things you’ve come to love us for, but with the addition of table service, a full bar, and a much larger space to tinker in, we have some room to “stretch” a bit (check the breakfast, lunch/dinner, and brunch menus attached)

If you scroll through you’ll see some great pics of the space courtesy of @randykrauseschmidt , menu and sign design (amongst other odds and ins) by the good people @opasigns , a killer neon via @bigsexyneon , and as always some amazing craftsmanship by @goodwoodnola - we also dropped in a few food pics from us. 

Y’all find some time to check them out, give them a follow or whatever, and I promise you’re gonna be blown away. Don’t keep this “our little secret”, and spread the word.
Merry Christmas y’all. We’re out at 2 today and off tomorrow. Stay safe and merry, and we’ll see you on Monday!

Can confirm: @cakecafenola cakes go hard. So good 😊. And bonus, while you’re in that part of town it’s hard not to grab a pizza lol. Eat ALL the cakes this season. #ddsbeats
We have 0-calorie king cake options too.

Whoever can name the most ingredients in our vegetarian burger (in one comment), we’ll hook you up with one on us. Wrong ingredients count against your score, and if by chance, someone names all the ingredients (they won’t), first to do so wins. You can not enter this contest if you make or have made our vegetarian burger 😂. Hint: it’s a lot of veggies, legumes, and grains. Contest ends at midnight

Ok, so about those vegetarian burgers. No one was perfect, but a few of y’all got suspiciously close lol: 
in it- roasted mushrooms, roasted eggplant, Black Beans, Garbanzo Beans, Beets, Yellow Onion, Jalapeño, Dates, Roasted Garlic, Brown Rice, Hot Cereal, Thyme, Salt, Paprika, Chile Powder, Black Pepper, Cumin, Potato Starch, Liquid Smoke, Molasses -on it: Havarti Cheese, Shredded Lettuce, Tomato, Mexicali pickled white onion, Roasted Tomato & Onion Aioli, Brioche Bun. 

We went ahead and grabbed a winner from IG and FB because we didn’t specify (check screen grabs). Great work everyone and congrats to the winners. Now, y’all come eat some vegetarian burgers. 

I’ll be hitting the winners up directly on the respective platforms
